15c4e0518eba9e4638ac8216683bf474dd362442860043a3a86837f1f0c058e0f8e53f2023cba3acc217d3f9301ccaa708c849b017628e123ce781b1b4acf621  0001-fix-cmake-add-the-qt6-suffix-to-the-lib-name-in-the-.patch
"
